column5: Certainly was a great show Dave put on.  They got my best side. The back of my hat
I see a few pics with me in my OFC colors where I am not suposed to go LOL.
how can you mistake that yellow coat mike!  iam in the first pic sittin beside the red pilar, black shades,OFC hat.
It was a good production - and the price was certainly right.  They got the back of my head in one of the london shots also  - didn't know there was quite that big a sunny patch back there ! : )))
